5:
All right. With that delivery out of the
way, we should be finished with the
requests from the Diviners'
Commission.
9:
Finally... We've been hiking all day
and I'm really starting to feel it...
14:
The sun is still high, shall we take a
brief rest?
21:
Yes, we are! I'll be with you in just a
moment!
25: Whoa, it's Alk and Light! Welcome!
33: So... Fuku got lost out here?
35:
We found her wandering around
near the store, so we decided to
take her in.
39:
They've been taking care of me,
which I really appreciate.
42: So... You're actually a child after all?
47:
A-adults can get lost sometimes,
too!
57:
Indeed. We haven't seen you around
in Starview Village for some time.
60:
I was beginning to get a little
worried.
63:
I'm so glad your family found you,
Fuku. It's time for you to go home
now, okay?
78:
You'll have to come back again
sometime.
83: I... I won't be coming back.
88:
Really? That girl... Koume, was it? She
seemed rather fond of you.
92:
What's wrong with going to meet a
friend?
98: And we can't be. I'm a yokai, after all.
103:
So? Humans and yokai can be
friends. Inaho's our friend, for
example!
105:
And it doesn't seem like it's such a
rare thing elsewhere, either.
109:
Yeah, but! I'm not just any yokai, I'm
a zashiki warashi...
112:
Humans are always after us
because they think we'll bring them
luck...
116:
Why don't you keep that part of
yourself a secret, then?
120:
B-but... You shouldn't keep secrets
from friends!
123:
I mean, having a friend you can talk
with about anything is great, but...
125:
Just because you can't share
everything with someone doesn't
mean they're not your friend.
128:
Oh, being intentionally deceitful isn't
good either, of course.
132: I wouldn't do anything like that!
135:
I know. Just share as much or as
little as you're comfortable with. Real
friends will understand.
145: I'll go back and see her again!
155: I'm... I'm okay! I know what to do now!
159:
All right. In that case, go and have
yourself some fun.
175:
That's 'cause I am! I brought a gift
from Koume's family!
180:
They gave me sweets from their
store and told me to share them
with everybody!
184: Wow! I guess I'll try one right away.
198:
Haha! At this rate, they'll be all gone
in no time!
203:
Then I guess I'll need to go visit them
again!
